{
  "stem": "17761.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 142.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people said that he used his-- his powers too much, or I don't know what is was exactly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't remember the names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I remember that there was a house for orphans, where children that were found in the streets and so on didn't know anybody, they were gathered in this house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and were taken care of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the leading figures were two brothers, also from that Gura-Humorului, with the name of Soniu Tauber-- T-A-U-B-E-R-- and Feivish Tauber.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They all were-- came-- they reached Israel afterwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they are not anymore around, but they passed away in Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They did a terrific world-- work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in this building where there was this [NON-ENGLISH], as we called it, for orphanage, there was also a synagogue on Rosh Hashanah, Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there, we used to go to listen to the prayers of a doctor called Dr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Rhode ?] who was a wonderful hazzan in addition to being a doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So until now, I remember certain things that I heard from that hazzan.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only organization that I remember was a general Zionist youth movement, which was underground, not official.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very few people knew about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to have certain activities in very small groups-- by two, by three, something like this-- because we didn't want to make any noise around it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We exchanged books.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was one of the activities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We sang songs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Things were-- songs were composed there in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I mentioned-- I would like to mention this respect-- a-- a guy who was from the [HEBREW] movement, who was the name of Tutiu Lablonower-- T-U-T-U-I-- T-U-T-U-- T-I-U I-A-B-L-O-N-O-W-E-R-- who had also a wonderful voice.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was from my place [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he is-- he's still living.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
